    <briefdescription>
<para>A class that combines characters through an indexed result matrix. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It uses supported Unicode code points and a compact byte matrix of result indexes. Unknown characters fall back to the overlay character. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
